title: Design for Citibank/Citicorp Logo
provenance: From the collection of Dan Friedman
medium: Brush and black ink, black marker, graphite on white tracing paper
description: Circular design centered on sheet consisting of a four pointed vertically oriented star motif, outlined in black with lozenge shaped black tips. This pattern is centered on a white, solidly drawn cross shape which floats in the center of a black circle.
